OL,3,CDisability ice skating rink hosts
OL,4,Cformer figure-skating world champion
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Andy Dickenson
OL,7,Fstayed behind the side boards as he
OL,8,Fvisited inclusive ice-skating in
OL,9,FEastbourne.
OL,11,FThe sport of ice skating has not
OL,12,Falways been accessible for people in
OL,13,Fwheelchairs - with narrow entrances to
OL,14,Fthe ice and a slippery service.
OL,16,FMore rinks have been renovating their
OL,17,Fsites to allow wheelchair users to
OL,18,Fexperience the sport they love,
OL,19,Fincluding Eastbourne's Lightning Fibre
OL,20,FIce Rink which opened to the public on
OL,21,F7 December.
