OL,3,CDisability ice skating rink hosts
OL,4,Cformer figure-skating world champion
OL,6,FBased in the Enterprise Shopping
OL,7,FCentre car park, the rink has aimed to
OL,8,Fbe inclusive, with a wider entrance
OL,9,Fand sessions for people with
OL,10,Fdisabilities.
OL,12,FThe charity Forward Facing - brought
OL,13,Falong some of the people it helps to
OL,14,Ftake to the ice, alongside an icon of
OL,15,Fthe sport.
OL,17,FFormer Dancing on Ice judge and
OL,18,FOlympic figure skating champion Robin
OL,19,FCousins MBE was in attendance at the
OL,20,Fevent, celebrating inclusivity in ice
OL,21,Fskating.
