OL,3,CDisability ice skating rink hosts
OL,4,Cformer figure-skating world champion
OL,6,FHe won the 1980 Winter Olympic title
OL,7,Fin figure skating, however, he
OL,8,Fbelieves pop-ups should not just be a
OL,9,Fpipeline for new Olympians.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's hugely important. Here
OL,12,Fyou see wheelchairs on the ice and now
OL,13,Fthere are a lot of ice-skating rinks
OL,14,Fabout that have wheelchair accessible
OL,15,Fsessions.
