OL,3,CDisability ice skating rink hosts
OL,4,Cformer figure-skating world champion
OL,6,F"If there is an ice rink that is a pop-
OL,7,Fup like this one, you will find that
OL,8,Fthe barrier space to enter and exit
OL,9,Fwill be big enough, and they will host
OL,10,Fspecific sessions (for wheelchair
OL,11,Fusers).
OL,13,F"Diversity is important, inclusivity
OL,14,Fis important, not only from a
OL,15,Frecreational point of view, but also
OL,16,Fat a Paralympics and Special Olympics
OL,17,Fpoint of view."
OL,19,FThe rink is open until 31 December
OL,20,F2024.
